27
00:01:08,378 --> 00:01:09,497
Who’s even called Stir-Fried Clams?

28
00:01:09,880 --> 00:01:10,761
Kang.

29
00:01:10,761 --> 00:01:12,014
My name is Kang.

30
00:01:12,123 --> 00:01:12,809
Kang.

31
