50
00:03:13,383 --> 00:03:15,220
Can I have this one?

51
00:03:15,220 --> 00:03:15,881
Just one.

52
00:03:21,726 --> 00:03:22,993
Hey, I only want one.

53
00:03:23,748 --> 00:03:25,640
Just eat and don’t complain.

54
00:03:25,640 --> 00:03:27,218
Only one is not enough.

55
00:03:27,218 --> 00:03:29,405
Eating a big breakfast will make you smart.

56
00:03:31,045 --> 00:03:31,935
Remember that.

57
00:03:31,935 --> 00:03:32,665
Here you go.

58
00:03:33,979 --> 00:03:34,703
Thank you.

59
00:03:40,702 --> 00:03:41,788
What can I get you?

60
00:03:56,601 --> 00:03:57,296
Hey!

61
00:03:58,816 --> 00:04:00,447
