66
00:04:12,939 --> 00:04:13,687
I thought it was trash.

67
00:04:13,687 --> 00:04:14,187
Hey.

68
00:04:14,187 --> 00:04:15,472
Are you trying to get on our nerves?

69
00:04:15,685 --> 00:04:16,648
Are you trying to get on our nerves?

70
