80
00:05:08,631 --> 00:05:09,603
I don’t have friends.

81
00:05:11,013 --> 00:05:12,360
Be careful.

82
00:05:12,360 --> 00:05:14,788
Those two are the school bullies.

83
00:05:14,939 --> 00:05:16,360
Don’t get into trouble with them.

84
00:05:17,173 --> 00:05:19,173
I’ll tell you something.

85
00:05:20,818 --> 00:05:22,927
Last year during a lunch break,

86
00:05:23,098 --> 00:05:26,096
something happened to a 12-grader named Plu who was known as the alpha kid.

87
00:05:26,451 --> 00:05:29,414
No one dared to mess with or defy him.

88
00:05:29,523 --> 00:05:30,872
Everyone could only join him

89
00:05:31,299 --> 00:05:33,299
and give way to him

90
00:05:33,499 --> 00:05:34,766
except…

91
00:05:34,766 --> 00:05:35,834
Who’s Potae?

92
00:05:37,164 --> 00:05:37,981
What’s the matter?

93
00:05:40,601 --> 00:05:44,000
You’re the one who broke my little sister Ploysai’s heart, right?

94
00:05:47,026 --> 00:05:48,483
You’re dead.

95
00:05:55,318 --> 00:05:56,393
The next morning,

96
00:05:57,615 --> 00:05:59,844
