175
00:10:56,525 --> 00:10:57,672
Whose toes did you step on this time?

176
00:10:57,672 --> 00:10:58,455
I did not.

177
00:10:58,455 --> 00:11:01,160
I guess they’re picking on me because I’m new.

178
00:11:01,160 --> 00:11:02,013
Luckily, I ran away first.

179
00:11:02,013 --> 00:11:02,640
I have to go.

180
00:11:03,131 --> 00:11:03,892
Moo is over there!

181
00:11:03,892 --> 00:11:05,131
Get him!

182
00:11:05,241 --> 00:11:05,834
Hey!

183
00:11:07,241 --> 00:11:08,648
Don’t fight in school!

184
00:11:08,648 --> 00:11:09,148
Quiet!

185
00:11:09,148 --> 00:11:10,256
- Let go of me!
- Go back to selling rice and curry.

186
00:11:10,256 --> 00:11:11,916
Let go of me!

187
00:11:12,041 --> 00:11:13,824
Kang!

188
00:11:13,881 --> 00:11:15,772
Help me, Kang!

189
00:11:17,178 --> 00:11:18,000
Let go!

190
00:11:18,163 --> 00:11:19,341
Let go! What are you doing to me?

191
00:11:20,513 --> 00:11:21,325
Let go of me!

192
00:11:21,325 --> 00:11:22,513
Let go of Moo!

193
00:11:22,513 --> 00:11:23,327
What did he do to you?

194
00:11:24,726 --> 00:11:25,766
What are you guys doing?

195
00:11:25,766 --> 00:11:26,726
Ganging up on him?

196
00:11:30,892 --> 00:11:31,821
Let go of me!

197
00:11:34,720 --> 00:11:35,791
Don’t come any closer!

198
00:11:36,550 --> 00:11:37,336
Don’t come any closer!

199
00:11:38,232 --> 00:11:41,440
Don’t come any closer!

200
00:11:41,440 --> 00:11:44,258
Don’t!

