00:11:48,925 --> 00:11:53,395
♪ I want you to try to understand ♪

202
00:11:53,395 --> 00:11:57,960
♪ I want to get through to your heart ♪

203
00:11:57,960 --> 00:12:02,222
♪ The more I try to stop, the faster my heart beats ♪

204
00:12:02,222 --> 00:12:07,785
♪ All I have is you in my heart ♪

205
00:12:11,784 --> 00:12:16,200
♪ Can I love you? How many scores do I get ♪

206
00:12:16,200 --> 00:12:18,884
♪ What should I do to be with you? I will do it all ♪

207
00:12:20,658 --> 00:12:24,857
♪ I’m still new to love, you’re my tutor ♪

208
00:12:24,857 --> 00:12:26,596
♪ Don’t care how much you score ♪

209
00:12:26,596 --> 00:12:30,196
♪ As long as we’re together, I will be fine ♪

210
00:12:36,000 --> 00:12:38,896
(Phew, I thought I was going to get beaten up.)

211
00:12:40,249 --> 00:12:41,567
Looks like everything is fine now.

212
00:12:42,000 --> 00:12:42,682
I’m leaving.

213
00:12:44,256 --> 00:12:44,927
Kang.

214
00:12:51,998 --> 00:12:53,159
We’re sorry, Master,

215
00:12:53,159 --> 00:12:55,464
for being rude to you this morning.

216
00:12:55,464 --> 00:12:57,243
We just found out who your mom is.

217
00:12:58,555 --> 00:13:01,520
We apologize for not knowing anything outside Nakhon Pathom.

218
00:13:03,404 --> 00:13:05,404
We were ignorant.

219
00:13:07,513 --> 00:13:12,000
Does our joke make you feel any better, Master?

220
00:13:12,000 --> 00:13:15,204
If not, please feel free to blame Tae.

221
00:13:15,204 --> 00:13:15,810
I have nothing to do with it.

222
00:13:18,935 --> 00:13:19,856
Well, you can blame me.

223
00:13:20,779 --> 00:13:25,920
Honestly, I’m still confused why you guys danced for me.

224
00:13:27,656 --> 00:13:30,000
We’d like some help, Master.

225
00:13:30,332 --> 00:13:33,360
Could you show our dance clip to your mom?

226
00:13:33,803 --> 00:13:36,916
We happen to be a dance group

227
00:13:37,050 --> 00:13:40,640
and your mom happens to be a producer

228
00:13:40,920 --> 00:13:45,960
so we’d really appreciate kindness and support from your mom.

229
00:13:46,890 --> 00:13:49,053
What a perfect coincidence, Master

230
00:13:49,292 --> 00:13:52,161
Could you ask your mom to consider helping us?

231
00:13:53,368 --> 00:13:56,560
So, you guys dragged me here

232
00:13:56,646 --> 00:13:57,686
to make me watch you dance?

233
00:13:59,080 --> 00:14:00,040
Yes.

234
00:14:01,435 --> 00:14:03,435
I thought I was being threatened.

235
00:14:03,477 --> 00:14:07,486
I thought you two were going to punch my face and break my arms like you did to that 12-grader.

236
00:14:09,405 --> 00:14:10,916
Here’s the true story, Master.

237
00:14:13,640 --> 00:14:15,640
Hey, calm down, bro!

238
00:14:16,272 --> 00:14:18,000
Don’t try to make an excuse.

239
00:14:18,000 --> 00:14:18,838
Hey, bro.

240
00:14:18,838 --> 00:14:20,279
You two are going to get it.

241
00:14:20,279 --> 00:14:21,385
Calm down, bro.

242
00:14:21,385 --> 00:14:22,513
Let’s talk nicely.

243
00:14:22,513 --> 00:14:23,674
Yes!

244
00:14:25,887 --> 00:14:27,127
Hey, come on!

245
00:14:27,679 --> 00:14:28,865
Come at me!

246
00:14:32,910 --> 00:14:34,430
More!

247
00:14:38,512 --> 00:14:39,682
Oh, shit!

248
00:14:40,251 --> 00:14:41,170
You’re going to get it!

249
00:14:51,051 --> 00:14:52,186
Shit!

250
00:14:55,498 --> 00:14:56,657
Is he dead?

251
00:14:58,286 --> 00:15:00,564
After that, Plu’s dad took him out of this school.

252
00:15:00,863 --> 00:15:04,454
It was an accident that allowed us to pretend to be powerful.

253
00:15:04,861 --> 00:15:06,963
Who wouldn’t take that golden opportunity?

254
00:15:08,796 --> 00:15:13,945
So there was no arm or leg breaking, right?

255
00:15:14,160 --> 00:15:15,807
Of course not, Master.

256
00:15:16,372 --> 00:15:18,209
We’re not thugs.

257
00:15:18,601 --> 00:15:22,240
Like we said, we prefer dancing and singing.

258
00:15:22,240 --> 00:15:24,783
We’ve been practicing for a year to audition.

259
00:15:24,783 --> 00:15:26,519
We go to every audition there is.

260
00:15:26,519 --> 00:15:28,789
We want a lot of people to see our talent.

261
00:15:28,967 --> 00:15:29,900
Really?

262
00:15:30,443 --> 00:15:31,510
Me too.

263
00:15:31,510 --> 00:15:32,177
Really?

264
00:15:32,177 --> 00:15:33,575
Would you like to dance with us then?

265
00:15:33,575 --> 00:15:34,225
Can I?

266
00:15:35,040 --> 00:15:36,904
Where do you guys normally dance?

267
00:15:36,904 --> 00:15:38,386
I’ve wanted someone to help with my dance moves for a few days now.

268
00:15:38,661 --> 00:15:39,920
Tae can help you with that, Master.

269
00:15:39,920 --> 00:15:40,918
That’s amazing, Master.

270
00:15:40,918 --> 00:15:41,645
Let me take you there.

271
00:15:50,243 --> 00:15:51,343
It’s just one semester.

272
00:15:51,343 --> 00:15:54,930
Go and study there so there’s no entertainment to distract you.

273
00:15:55,117 --> 00:15:59,120
Just focus on doing well in school and passing the university admission exam.

274
00:15:59,120 --> 00:16:00,608
That’s enough.

275
00:16:00,608 --> 00:16:01,351
End of story.

276
